which economic actors were subjected by members of FRCI and unidentified armed 
groups. This scourge also contributes to rising food prices, putting more pressure on a 
population that is already severely affected by the post-election crisis. He observed that the 
Government had begun dismantling unofficial checkpoints throughout the country. 
