Correction Centre. The physician was later provisionally released, along with two 
journalists imprisoned on the same charges.  
34. When asked about the sentiment of victor&#8217;s justice apparently felt by some inside 
and outside the country, prosecutor Kouadio said: &#8220;I will, if I am able to, send investigation 
